                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Share a link that feels like yours. No more email ping-pong.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-5 group hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300 p-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-white hover:shadow-lg">
                <i data-feather="shield" class="w-10 h-10 text-indigo-600 group-hover:text-indigo-500"></i>
                <div>
