        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">isked is more than a scheduling tool — it's your assistant, buffer, and time-saver rolled into one.</p>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-indigo-50 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                <div class="text-left">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">1-on-1 Consultations</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Make it easy for clients to find time with you. No confusion, no delays.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-indigo-50 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                <div class="text-left">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">Discovery Calls</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Let leads instantly book time to connect, without the wait.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-indigo-50 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                <div class="text-left">
