        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900">Let Others Book You — Without the Hassle</h2>
        <a href="/auth/register" class="mt-6 bg-indigo-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-indigo-700 inline-block shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:scale-105">
            Get Started for Free
